Package: GTA
Type: Package
Title: Genotoxicity Test Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Frank Bringezu, CPS Merck Healthcare KGaA, Darmstadt Germany
Maintainer: Frank Bringezu <frank.bringezu@merckgroup.com>
Description: A comprehensive package for analyzing genotoxicity test data,
    including micronucleus (MN) tests. Provides statistical analysis using
    Mann-Whitney U tests with Holm-Bonferroni correction, and includes a
    user-friendly Shiny dashboard for regulatory scientists.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
